StoredProcedureOraclev10g.name: GETSUBJECT
StoredProcedureOraclev10g.source: CREATE OR REPLACE PROCEDURE GRUPO10.GETSUBJECT(cSubject OUT SYS_REFCURSOR)&lt;br/&gt;IS&lt;br/&gt;BEGIN&lt;br/&gt; OPEN cSubject FOR &lt;br/&gt; SELECT Subject_table.idSubject, Subject_table.subjectName, Subject_table.credit,&lt;br/&gt; Subject_table.subjectPrerequisites, Subject_table.idPerson&lt;br/&gt; FROM Subject_table;&lt;br/&gt;END getSubject;
